    <title>乔治学习笔记</title>
    <link href="/2024/02/07/%E4%B9%94%E6%B2%BB%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
    <url>/2024/02/07/%E4%B9%94%E6%B2%BB%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文主要是乔治在学习编程中的学习笔记和个人作业</p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="第六节课"><a href="#第六节课" class="headerlink" title="第六节课"></a>第六节课</h2><h3 id="for循环"><a href="#for循环" class="headerlink" title="for循环"></a>for循环</h3><h4 id="模版格式"><a href="#模版格式" class="headerlink" title="模版格式"></a>模版格式</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs Java"><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(起始条件；终止条件；操作过程)&#123;<br>    需要做的事情；<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>使用for循环输出1到100</li></ul><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">a</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(a = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; a &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">100</span>; a = a + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) &#123;<br>System.out.println(a);<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>使用for循环计算1到100的和</li></ul><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs Java"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">a</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">b</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(a = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; a &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">100</span>; a = a + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) &#123;<br>b = b + a;<br>&#125;<br>System.out.println(b)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>乔治在这个过程里需要注意的是for循环的执行顺序，首先是进行第一步a&#x3D;1，然后b&#x3D;b+a，然后a&#x3D;a+1，然后再去判断a&lt;&#x3D;100，然后再次计算b&#x3D;b+a，这个执行顺序一定要清楚</p></blockquote><ul><li>使用for循环输出所有奇数</li></ul><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs Java"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">a</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(a = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; a &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">100</span>; a = a + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(a % <span class="hljs-number">2</span> == <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) &#123;<br>    System.out.println(a);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>上面讲了可以使用for循环输出1到100，那么输出所有奇数就要在这个基础上加一些判断条件，输出之前首先判断一下是否是奇数，如果是奇数，就输出，如果是偶数，就不输出，这样就使用for循环和if条件语句把这个问题解决了</p></blockquote><ul><li>使用for循环判断程序的执行次数</li></ul><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">a</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(a = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; a &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">5</span>; a = a + <span class="hljs-number">2</span>) &#123;<br>System.out.println(a)<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>可以自己把里面的条件改一下，例如改成a&#x3D;5；a&lt;&#x3D;25；a&#x3D;a+3，这种格式的，手动推一下输出过程，通过手动推导来清楚了解for循环的执行过程</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
    
